flowchart TD
    A[1. Upload Documents] --> B[2. Convert and Extract Text]
    B --> C{Large PDF?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Apply Memory Guard\nand Fallback Extraction]
    C -->|No| E[Standard Extraction]
    D --> F[3. Chunk Documents]
    E --> F
